{"tid":2195082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共媒體聲稱  中國駐澳洲記者住所曾遭搜查","createTime":"2020-09-09T02:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T05:31:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a6a9eef5127152dd11f3be5bc71ac11c2d27e30a","tid":2195082,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:53:18.000Z","msg":"報道指中國駐澳洲記者住所曾遭搜查<br />\n3小時前  Share to Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=404858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404858&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=c30bb0af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404858&h=468b0014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=404858</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】內地傳媒報道，澳洲搜查過多間中國媒體派駐當地記者的住所。<br />\n<br />\n中新社的報道指，澳洲的執法人員6月26日，以所謂涉嫌違反外國影響透明計劃法為理由，無端搜查三間中國媒體駐澳機構四名記者的住所，同時扣押手機、電腦，及文字材料等，最終證明有關中國記者並未從事與身分不符的活動。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，這些中國記者在澳洲期間一直遵守當地法律，澳方所謂「搜查」嚴重侵犯中國記者的合法權益，嚴重干擾中國媒體在澳洲正常的報道活動。報道質疑外國記者在一貫標榜新聞自由的澳洲遵紀守法、正常開展工作，為何會遭受如此對待。"},{"pid":"7ae7d74c1c1ace82a0aeb225af50de6ab6d1d5ac","tid":2195082,"uid":34534,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:54:16.000Z","msg":"因為佢地唔係記者<br />\n係作家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f734c7ccd0d948d2f54e060f6de84396faed4c2","tid":2195082,"uid":246465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a6a9eef5127152dd11f3be5bc71ac11c2d27e30a","tid":2195082,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:53:18.000Z","msg":"報道指中國駐澳洲記者住所曾遭搜查<br />\n3小時前  Share to Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=404858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404858